<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>... فَعَال، بفتح الفاء<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>و <span class="c4">[السَّخاء]</span>: الجود.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
